snippet.title: Signal Lost (Both Endings) - Indie Horror Game - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/Stella-Abbasi-100150965166877/
Twitter https://twitter.com/StellaAbbasi

Download https://endsmeet-production.itch.io/signallost

You play as Alex, a technician dispatched for an emergency night repair at a remote radio tower deep in the woods. What starts as a simple task quickly descends into a nerve-wracking nightmare when the signal you’re fixing begins broadcasting something... unnatural.

Indie Horror Game Playlist https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk0tZ0YT3FZEsIgd3Qdj19xGe9VcMMI1P

#signallost #Indiegames
